title: Riot send help pls, there are queue trolls in ranked for provs

replies.body: That alpha client is so dumbed down. Lots of relevant information missing. I wish they would have just kept the same structure of the legacy client even if they switched it over to the chromium engine.

You can submit feedback about the new client under the "Alpha" tab by pressing "Submit your feedback".

However I'm curious as to what you feel is missing from the new client, as all I'm aware of that is present in legacy but not in alpha is item sets, which to the best of my knowledge are on the way.

I don't see anything wrong?
I must be missing something
did you look at the image :l

I didn't see that sorry, It was hard for me to pick it out.
I just looked at scores build and if anything was said in chat.
3 smites! all the jungle objective control!
